<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>微专业HTML的单元作业1</title>
	<style type="text/css">
	    *{
	    	margin: 0;
	    	padding: 0;
	    }
	    h2{
	    	margin-left: 20px;
	    	margin-top: 20px;
	    }
		ul{
			width: 280px;
			margin-top: 20px;
			margin-left: 20px;
			list-style: none;
		}
		li{
			border-top: 1px dotted #ccc;
			padding: 10px 0 10px 10px;
		}
		li:first-child{
			border-top: 2px solid #ccc;
		}
		a:hover{
			color: red;
		}
		a{
			text-decoration: none;
			color: black;
			font-size: 20px;
		}
		a span{
			color: red;
		}


	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div>
		<h2>图书畅销榜</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><a href="#" title="当我足够好，才会遇见你"><span>1</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;当我足够好，才会遇见你</a></li>
			<li><a href="#" title="皮囊"><span>2</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;皮囊</a></li>
			<li><a href="#" title="李光耀论中国与世界"><span>3</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;李光耀论中国与世界</a></li>
			<li><a href="#" title="乖，摸摸头">4&nbsp;&nbsp;乖，摸摸头</a></li>
			<li><a href="#" title="男女内参">5&nbsp;&nbsp;男女内参</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
